# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Configuration file for the rEFIt (Clover) boot menu
# Customized for mrenglesTheme by Mrengles.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Timeout in seconds for the main menu screen. Commenting the timeout
# option or setting it to -1 disables automatic booting (i.e., no timeout).
# Setting it to 0 enables direct boot to default volume.
#
# timeout 15  - The default setting for mrenglesTheme
# timeout 5   - Enter menu and wait for 5 sec to boot default Volume
# timeout 0   - Boot into default volume without GUI
# timeout -1  - Enter GUI without default booting 
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
timeout 15
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The next 4 settings allow mrenglesTheme to become the default,
# while loading and setting the correct font file and width.
# Nothing else to see here, keep on moving down the page.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DON'T CHANGE THESE SETTINGS UNLESS YOU KNOW EXACTLY WHAT YOUR DOING.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
theme mrengles
font load
font_file_name mrenglesTheme.png
char_width 10
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# You can change the Clover (rEFIT) main menu logo here. Make sure your
# commenting "#" is correct or you could have issue with your next boot.
#
# Clover_Logo.png		- The default setting for mrenglesTheme
# Transparent_Logo.png	- Still testing as of Clover r832 (BETA)
# No_Logo.png			- Just like it says No logo, or F1 help reminder. =)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
banner Clover_Logo.png
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Setting the correct background size & fill pattern will effect the quality
# of artwork/graphics at the main menu. Pattern options [crop][tile][scale].
# Try to create your own background and save to mrenglesTheme folder:
# /EFI/BOOT/themes/mrenglesTheme/CustomName.png
#
# background Background.png tile	- The default setting for mrenglesTheme
# background CustomName.png tile	- Your custom Background image
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
background Background.png tile
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The next 7 settings are required for mrenglesTheme. They are set this
# way for a reason. Nothing else to see here, keep on moving down the page.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DON'T CHANGE THESE SETTINGS UNLESS YOU KNOW EXACTLY WHAT YOUR DOING.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
selection_small Selection_64px.png
selection_big Selection_144px.png
selection_color 0x0a0a0a99
hidebadges all
hideui badges
quiet

# ==========================================================================
# Enable the use of the log file (/efi/misc/system.log)
#systemlog
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# List legacy options first. When enabled, legacy BIOS based boot options
# (e.g. Windows, Linux via LILO or GRUB) will be listed first. This is
# intended as a quick fix to change the default boot choice until full
# configurability arrives.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# legacyfirst
# nolegacy
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EOF
